    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>兵连祸结</strong>是一款以小队为单位的单人游戏，玩家在游戏中扮演被赶出家园的姐妹雅拉和艾兰妮，她们必须穿越战火纷飞的塔劳群岛，到达安全的贝农，她们祖先的堡垒。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>系统元素系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兵连祸结的特色是使用火、水、焦油、植物和闪电等元素的系统化、新兴游戏系统。策略性地选择你的小队，驾驭各种元素和环境，对抗成群的敌人。水能灭火，焦油能增强火力，电能在潮湿的环境中噼啪作响，水能治疗植物类单位。这还只是表面现象！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/0cfa7fb2179c0834227dd867c6a2c4d9.poster.avif?t=1763074233\" width=609 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/0cfa7fb2179c0834227dd867c6a2c4d9.webm?t=1763074233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基于小队的战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在环游世界的旅程中，招募哥布林、精灵、恶魔、树人等奇幻生物小队来组建你的商队。每支队伍凭借独特特性与专属技能，为你的商队增添全新战术选择。灵活搭配参战队伍，方能真正掌控征途。战场站位、队伍组合与技能运用皆可扭转战局，但需谨记：每场败绩都将消耗士气，若商队丧失希望，游戏即告终结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/62adc9f95f687c5ed2975294eb670479.poster.avif?t=1763074233\" width=609 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/62adc9f95f687c5ed2975294eb670479.webm?t=1763074233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战略可重复性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏融合了战略和roguelite元素，具有很强的可重复性，每次运行都会有新鲜感，这要归功于新出现的游戏玩法、动态小队管理和不可预测的叙事事件，这些事件可能会拯救你苦苦挣扎的乐队，也可能会让他们丧命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/2082024995bc45eafa5ea651c659d0b5.poster.avif?t=1763074233\" width=609 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/2082024995bc45eafa5ea651c659d0b5.webm?t=1763074233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>找到你失散的家人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜索塔劳尔群岛（Isles of Talaur），与雅拉和埃兰妮的家人见面，他们会揭示游戏故事的片段，并授予玩家传家宝，为玩家今后的游戏带来新的优势和能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >/r/n</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索世界地图</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索世界地图，它展示了你的旅程的巨大规模。这里有分支路径和意想不到的结果，每一个选择都会带来新的挑战。一定要注意你的希望、你的食物，并照顾好你的小队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/9a326083c828621ecdbfb3e7a3dbfe94.poster.avif?t=1763074233\" width=800 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/9a326083c828621ecdbfb3e7a3dbfe94.webm?t=1763074233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1296660/extras/9a326083c828621ecdbfb3e7a3dbfe94.mp4?t=1763074233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
